      <td><strong>Schema Flexibility</strong></td>
      <td>Rigid or flexible schema depending on database type</td>
      <td>Pre-defined and fixed schema definition for ingest (schema on write and read)</td>
      <td>No schema definition required for ingest (schema on read)</td>
    </tr>
